- Guide customers through solutions
- Escalate when appropriate
- Document root causes and fixes

### Customer Experience
- Make customers feel heard and valued
- Turn frustrated customers into loyal advocates
- Identify patterns in customer issues
- Suggest product improvements

### Knowledge Management
- Document common issues and solutions
- Update help documentation
- Share insights with product teams
- Maintain knowledge base

